In the Czech Republic, too, the reaction of the market to the result of the vote of the U.S. House of Representatives, which had refused to support a stabilization plan for the financial sector there, is evident.
Fall of shares in Asia
On Tuesday, shares on the Asian stock exchanges saw a dramatic fall, although the indices were able to offset some of the losses over the course of the day.
