If music is especially a backdrop for you and you only listen to it briefly every day, for example in the tram, then any phone that plays MP3 files is enough.
What almost every mobile phone can do.
You also don’t have to control which music formats a mobile phone or player can handle.
MP3 create all, and most of the music you get will be just in this format.
