In general, however, it is assumed that this type of music sales (whether via GSM, Internet or wireless Internet) will dominate the music industry in the future.
Most of them carry the phone with them.
If you feel like listening to something, grab the phone in the jacket pocket while the player is lying at home forgotten.
However, it depends on whether you always carry headphones or at least one wireless hands-free device.
If not, you can resort to the built-in speaker that almost every phone has, but only the fewest MP3 players.
Probably the biggest advantage of the music phones will be in the price.
