Brussels had commissioned the independent scientific committee in view of the widespread use of portable music equipment among young people.
"The scientists confirm that one is rightly concerned and that the European Commission, together with the other EU Member States and those concerned, will now examine the necessary measures to better protect children and young people from the noise that comes from portable music and similar devices."
